      <title>谢因鲍姆选择延续墨西哥最新内阁人选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/sheinbaum-opts-for-continuity-with-latest-mexico-cabinet-picks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆任命罗莎·伊塞拉·罗德里格斯为墨西哥内政部长，此举标志着她在安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔大约三个月后离任前的过渡期中取得了连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/sheinbaum-opts-for-continuity-with-latest-mexico-cabinet-picks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 19:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟警告匈牙利总统奥尔班不要计划访问俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/eu-warns-hungary-s-orban-against-plan-to-visit-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲理事会主席查尔斯·米歇尔警告欧盟轮值主席国匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班不要代表欧盟与俄罗斯对话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/eu-warns-hungary-s-orban-against-plan-to-visit-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 18:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Netflix、派拉蒙请求加拿大法院撤销特鲁多新税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/netflix-paramount-ask-canada-court-to-quash-trudeau-s-new-levy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国流媒体服务巨头正在请求加拿大法院阻止加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多对其在该国的收入征收 5% 的新税，这笔税原本用于资助当地新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/netflix-paramount-ask-canada-court-to-quash-trudeau-s-new-levy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 18:01:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大投资数百万美元建设芯片网络，美国紧随其后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-invests-millions-to-build-chip-network-as-us-races-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将在五年内投资 1.2 亿加元（8820 万美元）建设国家芯片网络，与此同时，要求政府采取更多措施支持其落后的半导体行业的呼声越来越高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-invests-millions-to-build-chip-network-as-us-races-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:35:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 X 因危险内容收到欧盟的最终警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/musk-s-x-to-get-final-eu-warning-over-dangerous-content</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于未能打击危险内容，埃隆·马斯克的社交媒体平台 X 将受到正式警告，这是欧盟监管机构最近几周第三次对大型科技公司采取强硬措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/musk-s-x-to-get-final-eu-warning-over-dangerous-content</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:19:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰央行行长将宽松预期推迟至 2026 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/poland-s-central-bank-chief-throws-easing-expectations-into-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰央行行长强化了其对通胀的立场，称政策制定者不太可能在 2026 年之前降息，因为他们预计物价将再次上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/poland-s-central-bank-chief-throws-easing-expectations-into-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:16:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士与欧盟重启金融市场监管谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/switzerland-and-eu-resume-talks-on-financial-market-regulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士与欧盟委员会已恢复有关金融市场监管的讨论，该讨论自 2017 年以来一直处于暂停状态，双方希望达成一项更广泛的协议来管理两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/switzerland-and-eu-resume-talks-on-financial-market-regulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 16:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示勒庞将无法获得法国多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-set-to-fall-short-of-majority-in-france-polling-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据民意调查公司的预测，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟在周日的法国立法选举中将无法获得绝对多数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/le-pen-set-to-fall-short-of-majority-in-france-polling-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大在美国报复威胁下实施数字服务税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国警告称将采取贸易报复措施，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府仍批准对大型外国科技公司征收数字服务税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在危机会议后赢得民主党州长的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/biden-wins-democratic-governors-backing-after-crisis-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在白宫举行的一次危机会议后，主要民主党州长对总统乔·拜登及其竞选连任表示了迄今为止最强烈​​的支持，据说这位 81 岁的老人在会上承认，他将不得不减少工作时间以避免疲劳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/biden-wins-democratic-governors-backing-after-crisis-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 00:20:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
